The paper proposes a new method for uncertainty estimation in large deep-learning models using natural gradient and variational inference. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural networks (cs.NE), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
